%e
%e

This GUI is used to help read data points off of a graph.
First, select known data points from the graph and enter the graph values into the corresponding edit boxes.
Then click the ''Points'' button to select desired data points. The x,y data pairs will be displayed in the GUI. When done, right click and the series of points will be output to the terminal.
The ''Get Axis'' button may be used to get axis data for use if you later want to plot data over the image with the same scale.
